						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone set up near the Siddharāmēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>[1452 A.D.] </p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated Śaka 1[3]73, Prajōtpati, Māgha, śu. 3, Sunday. The date corresponds with A.D. 1452, January 3, Tuesday (if śu) or February 8, Tuesday (if ba).</p>						

						<p>It states that the inscribed stone was set up by Hoṁnappa, son of Chaṁḍe-Nāyaka.</p>						

						</summary>
